# How To Disable Interchange


You will face an issue while upgrading version from 11.36 to 11.38 if  interchange is enabled. Because interchange was removed from cPanel & WHM in version 11.38.

**Error** 

```
[20130712.135246] E Blocker found: Cannot upgrade because Interchange is installed.
[20130712.135246] ***** FATAL: An attempt to up/downgrade to 11.38.1.6 was blocked. Please review blockers.
[20130712.135246]   The Administrator will be notified to review this output when this script completes
[20130712.135246] E Detected events which require user notification during updatenow. Will send iContact the log
=> Log closed Fri Jul 12 13:52:46 2013
=> Log closed Fri Jul 12 13:52:46 2013
```

We can disable it in WHM version 11.36.

- Go into WHM, Server Setup > Tweak Settings.
- Towards the middle in the software section is an option to disable interchange.

```diagram

```

Also, ensure that it is deselected in WHM > Service Manager.
